1
00:00:57,360 --> 00:01:00,240
I have dispatched troops to Wuse City

2
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:03,080
and ordered Jiuying to accompany them

3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,560
to capture the High Priest and Helian Jie

4
00:01:08,039 --> 00:01:10,360
to vent the anger for Your Highness.

5
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,730
No wonder he didn't show up.

6
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,880
He went to Wuse City

7
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,920
to capture people from the Helian clan.

8
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:20,240
I have adopted him for years

9
00:01:20,600 --> 00:01:22,320
and taught him everything.

10
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:25,000
If he dares to betray me,

11
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:28,560
I will make him die without a burial place.

12
00:01:29,160 --> 00:01:30,400
He is now

13
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:33,000
unable to protect himself.

14
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,680
If you're waiting for him to come back and save you,

15
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:38,240
you'll be waiting forever.

16
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,600
Besides, you want my military tally

17
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:43,759
just to get the military power of the Northern Frontier.

18
00:01:43,759 --> 00:01:44,920
But the Northern Frontier army

19
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:47,720
cannot be mobilized by a mere tally.

20
00:01:48,039 --> 00:01:49,880
Without my order,

21
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:53,039
no one will listen to you.

22
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,400
Then will you listen to me?

23
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,100
I heard there is a rumor in the capital

24
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:09,320
that I abducted the Empress Dowager.

25
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,520
A lie repeated often enough becomes the truth.

26
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,080
I am truly wronged.

27
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:16,000
I am utterly loyal.

28
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:19,160
This is forcing me into rebellion.

29
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:21,400
Your Grace,

30
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:22,920
how about this?

31
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,720
How about you marry me?

32
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,440
These are the betrothal gifts.

33
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,360
If you marry me,

34
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:32,240
I will help you return to the capital to seize power.

35
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,120
At that time,

36
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,480
we can crown the Ninth Prince as the child emperor.

37
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,680
You rule from behind the curtain.

38
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,640
I will be the regent.

39
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,300
Your Highness,

40
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:44,920
what do you think?

41
00:02:46,880 --> 00:02:49,200
Men in this world are ridiculous.

42
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:53,400
They always think they can control a woman with marriage.

43
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:57,160
I didn't expect Baili Jinghong to be no exception.

44
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,280
An eight-bearer sedan chair.

45
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,440
A grand wedding.

46
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,140
Proper etiquette.

47
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,810
None of them can be missing.

48
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:13,720
As Your Highness wishes.

49
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,360
Hahaha.

50
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,079
Why did you do this?

51
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:34,760
Are you asking why he saved me,

52
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,680
or why I saved you?

53
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,400
He saved me out of love.

54
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:48,900
I saved you because you are my older brother.

55
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:52,200
That bitch Shen Lian,

56
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:53,880
humiliated our father back then,

57
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,810
and now is using you to threaten me.

58
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,400
Impossible.

59
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:01,120
Wake up, brother.

60
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:06,820
Do you really think she suddenly found her conscience and treats you as a son?

61
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,450
She's just using your background,

62
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,820
and using my feelings for you.

63
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:15,680
She threatened me to hand over gold to her every year,

64
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,560
otherwise she would expose your Helian identity,

65
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,519
leaving you nowhere to go.

66
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,530
Impossible.

67
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,960
Hahaha.

68
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:30,880
Hahaha.

69
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,960
Nothing is impossible.

70
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,690
She thinks she's the smartest.

71
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,840
She thinks I'll be manipulated by her.

72
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:39,159
In her dreams.

73
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,440
Brother,

74
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,960
you are too naive.

75
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:48,560
Why do you think the truth of the gold corruption case could never be found out?

76
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:51,820
Do you really think this only has to do with Baili Jinghong?

77
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:53,120
Let me tell you.

78
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:55,159
Besides Shen Lian,

79
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,680
there is the new emperor Ji Hongzhen,

80
00:04:56,680 --> 00:05:00,480
and countless vampires hiding in the shadows of the Great Yin court.

81
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,600
Ji Hongzhen.

82
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,200
Ji Hongzhen.

83
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:09,200
He is really formidable.

84
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,040
Watching us fight to the death,

85
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,700
he enjoys the show in the dark.

86
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,600
Now that I'm useless,

87
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:18,120
he turns around and summons the imperial doctor away,

88
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,760
to cut off my way to survive.

89
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,840
Father was right.

90
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:28,120
No one can save the Helian clan.

91
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,400
No one.

92
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,760
No one.

93
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,159
You...

94
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:38,640
You actually serve three masters.

95
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:42,040
Who do I serve three masters for?

96
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,880
You have your ways,

97
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,760
and I have mine.

98
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:52,080
Does father know?

99
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,640
Do the clan elders know?

100
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,000
Of course.

101
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,800
Aman.

102
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,690
Overusing the forbidden arts,

103
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:03,520
will cause the clan members to die of exhaustion.

104
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,320
You guys...

105
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,720
So what?

106
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:09,840
Brother,

107
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:12,760
People are of high and low birth,

108
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:15,130
and goods are of different grades.

109
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,320
Dead is dead.

110
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:21,200
There will always be living people to take their place.

111
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:22,260
That's just great.

112
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,520
How is this behavior

113
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,900
any different from the court oppressing and enslaving us?

114
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:32,120
You are the young master of the Helian clan.

115
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:35,420
How can you be the same as them?

116
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,520
Eldest Master.

117
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:41,820
Eldest Master.

118
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,000
Eldest Master,

119
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,280
the general has mobilized troops to surround the Helian Manor,

120
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,480
and Wuse City as well.

121
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,760
He also ordered the arrest of all Helian clan members.

122
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,360
I have dispatched the hidden army

123
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:55,800
to escort all the citizens to a safe place.

124
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:57,720
But the Northern Border Army has entered the city.

125
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,440
It's only a matter of time before they are found.

126
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:00,700
We can't wait anymore.

127
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:01,930
Start the uprising.

128
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,340
But your poison...

129
00:07:05,280 --> 00:07:06,760
I am cured of the poison.

130
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,240
Mother.

131
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,520
Mingyue.

132
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,290
Wait for me to come back.

133
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,000
You must wait for me.

134
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:39,900
Your Highness.

135
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:46,060
Are you really going to marry him?

136
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,930
I need his soldiers,

137
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,980
and the sooner the better.

138
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:55,800
Otherwise,

139
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:58,000
once Ji Hongzhen secures the throne,

140
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,200
if I don't want to die,

141
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:02,370
I'll be forced to be his plaything.

142
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,320
But I refuse.

143
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,140
Your Highness.

144
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,650
The general said

145
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,450
tomorrow is an auspicious day.

146
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,600
Got it.

147
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,760
If you don't like Wu Lie,

148
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,440
from now on,

149
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,159
just stay by my side.

150
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,580
Thank you, Your Highness.

151
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:42,679
Huo Lingyu.

152
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:44,800
Tomorrow,

153
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,660
I'll trouble you to escort me for my wedding.

154
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,600
Brother.

155
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,640
I didn't expect you to hide

156
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:57,040
so many trusted aides in the Northern Army.

157
00:09:58,360 --> 00:10:01,760
The Dayin royal family has bullied our Helian clan for years.

158
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:05,080
Over the years,

159
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:11,080
I've also gathered evidence of officials forming self-serving factions.

160
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,860
With us brothers joining forces,

161
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,560
we'll completely overthrow

162
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,520
Dayin.

163
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:35,080
Eldest Young Master.

164
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:35,880
Bad news.

165
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,640
The Empress Dowager is marrying Baili Jinghong.

166
00:10:38,640 --> 00:10:40,200
The wedding is tomorrow.

167
00:10:47,040 --> 00:10:47,960
Brother.

168
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:57,680
I've done everything I should.

169
00:10:58,160 --> 00:10:59,480
Now that you are dead,

170
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:04,000
I have no reason to stay in the Helian clan.

171
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:42,760
Huo Lingyu.

172
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:44,560
I didn't expect

173
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:46,250
you to have such a skill.

174
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:48,680
My mother loved painting her nails,

175
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,800
but she didn't like nail polish.

176
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:55,380
She preferred using crushed impatiens to dye them.

177
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,960
The servants were careless

178
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:00,240
and always got the flower paste outside her nails,

179
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,840
which made her angry and cry.

180
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,560
I couldn't bear to see my mother sad,

181
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,730
so I learned to help her.

182
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,840
I couldn't save your mother.

183
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:15,880
I'm sorry.

184
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,960
You already tried your best.

185
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:37,080
Today is truly a joyous day.

186
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,840
We finally get to attend the General's wedding banquet.

187
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,880
Isn't it?

188
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,640
It's the General's wedding.

189
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:49,280
Why hasn't the Young General shown up?

190
00:12:49,280 --> 00:12:50,280
He went to patrol the border.

191
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:51,540
He should be back soon.

192
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:53,840
I doubt he'll be back.

193
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:57,500
I heard the Empress Dowager is quite fond of the Young General.

194
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:58,920
The General was furious,

195
00:12:58,920 --> 00:12:59,920
so...

196
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,720
Move the boxes inside.

197
00:13:02,920 --> 00:13:03,850
Watch your step.

198
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,920
Everything is ready.

199
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,280
So beautiful.

200
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,280
Your Majesty.

201
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,820
The auspicious hour has arrived.

202
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:13,080
The auspicious hour has arrived.

203
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:15,400
Bring in the bride and groom.

204
00:14:24,880 --> 00:14:29,040
First bow to Heaven and Earth.

205
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:36,080
Second bow to parents.

206
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:46,560
Husband and wife bow to each other.

207
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:54,440
Ceremony complete.

208
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:56,160
Congratulations, General.

209
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:58,000
Congratulations, General.

210
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,520
Congratulations, General.

211
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:02,320
Today

212
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:05,840
is my, Baili Jinghong's, wedding day.

213
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,800
I also announce to you all,

214
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:11,800
that the traitor Ji Hongzhen usurped the throne.

215
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:13,800
The late Emperor

216
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:16,610
left another edict of succession,

217
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:18,530
which is in the hands of my wife,

218
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:22,360
the Empress Dowager.

219
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:24,400
After tomorrow,

220
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:26,960
our Northern Army

221
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:30,680
will pick a date to march to the capital

222
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,960
to restore order.

223
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:43,640
To restore order!

224
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:46,600
Escort them to the bridal chamber.

225
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:49,000
Great.

226
00:16:05,280 --> 00:16:07,320
Great.

227
00:16:08,160 --> 00:16:10,160
Great.

228
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:13,680
Great.

229
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:16,680
Hahaha.

230
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,360
Great.
